definitions.definition: An injury to part of the body, most especially the brain , caused by a violent blow, followed by loss of function .
definitions.label_groups: uncountable in Commonwealth , countable in Canada , US

definitions.definition: The unlawful forcing of another by threats of violence to yield up something of value.

main_definition: ( obsolete , seismology ) A violent collision or shock .
